0.005 2023-12-13

  This is the last release done on CPAN. Development is moved to
  Debian's gitlab:
  https://salsa.debian.org/perl-team/modules/packages/libdist-zilla-app-command-authordebs-perl

  Bug fix:
    * remove --update-control which has Debian only dependencies

0.004 2023-12-10

  New features:
    * add --update-control option to udpate debian/control file
    * add --missing option to match authordeps (with a 'p') behavior
    * add --verbose option

  Bug fixes:
    * Avoid duplicates in the list of required debian packages

  Misc change:
    * depends on Config::Model::Dpkg

0.003 2016-12-12

